message.body: Hey hunter! Turns out my kale seeds are not at the green house, so can I start these varieties for to instead: rainbow chard, mustard, beets, calendula
Get some extra cool season biodiversity going on
I have some radish seeds you can seed as well
And lots if nitrogen fixing cover crop to amend other areas for next years nightshade a
Hey do u have a camping hammock I could borrow?
Sry for the barrage of texts
Hey. I don't loan my hammock. Sorry. I also don't have a bunch of room in my garden but some chard or mustard would be great. Thanks
I've got a wenzel u could borrow
